### Installation Guide

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AI-Cloud-Tech-Inc/AI-Empower-Hub-360-NC.git
cd AI-Empower-Hub-360-NC
```

2. Create a virtual environment:

```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
```

3. Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

4. Configure environment:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your configuration
```

5. Run the application:

```bash
python -m src.main
```

### Development Setup

Run tests:

```bash
pytest
```

Run with coverage:

```bash
pytest --cov=src
```

